<sentence type="quasi">▲旭川市<ruby rubyText="かぐら">神楽</ruby><ruby rubyText="おか">岡</ruby>〈→<enclosedCharacter>地</enclosedCharacter>ｐ．１４３，１５１〉</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
